
Webskola.lv School NodeJS Tutorial
Simple REST API application

1. initialize the MariaDB(mySQL) database first (e.g. using XAMPP)
    1a. see models/user.sql for user table
    1b. see config/db.config.js for database
2. npm start
3. Go to localhost:3000/api/users
4. develop the project further independently



Routing - %server%/api

URL             Method 	 	Action

api/users       POST	    add new user
api/users       GET 	    get all users
...
app/users/:id   GET         get user by id
app/users/:id   DELETE      delte user by id
...






